## Target Schema (analysis-ready)

The cleaned, joined, analysis-ready dataset used by both the paper and the product.

### [Main entity — e.g. KelurahanRecord]

```typescript
interface KelurahanRecord {
  // Identifiers
  kelurahan_id: string        // BPS area code — primary join key
  kelurahan_name: string      // Display name
  kecamatan: string           // District
  kota: string                // City

  // Primary variables
  transit_score: number       // Composite accessibility index [0–100]
  poverty_rate: number        // % population below poverty line (BPS 2020)

  // Control variables
  population_density: number  // persons per km²
  area_km2: number            // Area in square kilometers

  // Metadata
  data_year: number           // Source year
  has_missing: boolean        // Any imputed fields?
}
```

| Field | Type | Range / Values | Source | In paper | In product | Nullable |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| `kelurahan_id` | string | BPS code format | BPS | ✓ | ✓ | No |
| `transit_score` | float | 0–100 | Computed | ✓ | ✓ | No |
| `poverty_rate` | float | 0–1 | BPS 2020 | ✓ | ✓ | Yes* |

*Imputed using kecamatan median where missing.

