## Wrangling Transformations

Key transformations from raw → target schema:

| Target field | Source field(s) | Transformation |
|---|---|---|
| `kelurahan_id` | `kode_kelurahan` | rename only |
| `transit_score` | multiple GTFS fields | weighted composite formula — see methodology.md §2.5 |
| `poverty_rate` | `pct_miskin` | divide by 100 to normalize 0–1 |

---

## Mock Data Spec

For prototype development, `lib/mock-data.ts` must:
- Use the exact field names from the Target Schema above
- Use realistic value ranges (see Range column)
- Include at least 20 records for meaningful chart rendering
- Include a few records with nullable fields set to null (to test null handling)
- Include edge cases: min value, max value, one outlier

